title: The Physician 2013 720p DVDrip (greek subs) by kozanitis
description:
Mia exairetiki tainia epoxis, pou anakalypsa tyxaia tis teleutaies meres. Dystyxos then vrika amesos sostous ellinikous ypotitlous. Etsi anagastika na metafraso tous agglikous ypotitlous monos mou. Einai i proti mou prospathia sto xoro auto kai elpizo na tous vreite kalous.

Veltiosa tin poiotita tou video, thiorthonontas kyrios ti fotinotita kai tin antithesi kai sas to prosfero se analysi 720p: 1024x440 me tous dikous mou ellinikous ypotitlous.

An sas aresoun oi tainies epoxis einai sigouro oti tha perasete 2 euxaristes ores.

Kali diaskedasi.
